          alert("This is something very simple I made in dedication to Star Wars The Clone Wars since a seventh season is on the way and I can't wait, the Clone Wars series introduced Star Wars to me, and in my opinion is by far the best Star Wars piece you can get the movies does not come close to it ^^");
